# Layout Patterns (MANDATORY)

## Responsive Design (REQUIRED)
You MUST follow mobile-first patterns:

```typescript
<div className="
  w-full max-w-sm mx-auto       // Mobile: constrained
  sm:max-w-md                   // Small: wider
  lg:max-w-4xl lg:mx-0         // Large: full width
  grid grid-cols-1 gap-4       // Mobile: single column
  lg:grid-cols-3 lg:gap-6      // Large: three columns
">
  <SessionStats className="lg:col-span-3" />
  <PracticeFilters />
  <TranslationInput className="lg:col-span-2" />
</div>
```

## Standard Page Composition (MANDATORY)
You MUST follow this standard page layout pattern:

```typescript
// REQUIRED: Standard page layout pattern
<PageLayout pageTitle="Practice" pageIcon={Play}>
  {/* 1. Session Stats - Always first */}
  <SessionStats {...statsProps} />
  
  {/* 2. Filters - Always second */}
  <PracticeFilters {...filterProps} />
  
  {/* 3. Main Content - Always third */}
  <div className="max-w-4xl mx-auto w-full">
    <PageSpecificContent />
    <ActionButtons {...buttonProps} />
  </div>
</PageLayout>
```

## FORBIDDEN Layout Practices
- Non-responsive design patterns
- Custom layout patterns without component reusability